import React from 'react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <nav className="navbar">
      <Link to="/about" className="btn">
        About
      </Link>
      <Link to="/products" className="btn">
        Product
      </Link>
    </nav>
  )
}

export default Navbar
